name: Workflow Admin Web Content Display
description: Any description you want over here.

steps.name: I sign in to Liferay Portal as "test@liferay.com"

elements.name: Approve Web Content Via Web Content Display

steps.name: I go to "Content" > "Web Content" in the Product Menu
I configure workflow via folder info for "Single Approver (Version 1)"
I add a new page named "Web Content Display Page"
I add a "Web Content Display" portlet to the page
I add the following Web Content with workflow via Web Content Display
I should see the following Web Content is "Pending (Review)"
I go to "My Account" > "My Workflow Tasks" in the User Menu
